---

<Base title="speedrunning" description="Speedrunning — hollygorock.com">
  <h1>// SPEEDRUNNING</h1>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-title">// STATUS</div>
    <table class="ident-table">
      <tr>
        <td class="label">profile</td>
        <td><a href="https://www.speedrun.com/users/hollygorock" target="_blank" rel="noopener">speedrun.com/users/hollygorock</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="label">world records</td>
        <td class="status-active">22</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-title">// CURRENT FOCUS</div>
    <p>Working through individual levels in <strong>Excitebike (NES)</strong> with an eye toward a full game run. Also experimenting with <strong>Super Mario Bros.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <h2>// PERSONAL BESTS</h2>

  <div class="pb-table-wrap">
    <table class="pb-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>game</th>
          <th>category</th>
          <th>time</th>
          <th>rank</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {pbs.map(run => (
          <tr class={run.place === 1 ? 'wr' : ''}>
            <td>{run.game}</td>
            <td>{run.category}</td>
            <td class="time">{fmt(run.time)}</td>
            <td class="place">
              {run.place === 1 ? <span class="wr-badge">WR</span> : `#${run.place}`}
            </td>
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <a href="/projects" class="back">&lt; back to projects</a>
</Base>

<style>
  .ident-table {
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .ident-table tr + tr td { padding-top: 0.4rem; }
  .label {
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-right: 2rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    min-width: 8rem;
  }
  .status-active { color: var(--green); }

  .pb-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }

  .pb-table {
    border-collapse: collapse;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .pb-table th {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-weight: normal;
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .pb-table td {
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .pb-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .pb-table tr.wr td { color: var(--amber-glow); }

  .time { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; white-space: nowrap; }
  .place { white-space: nowrap; color: var(--muted); }

  .wr-badge {
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: 0.45rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  strong { color: var(--amber-glow); font-weight: normal; }

  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .back:hover { color: var(--amber); }
</style>
